@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# Sync Carbon Inventory Lines - Batch create, update, and delete operations
# This endpoint allows atomic synchronization of multiple line changes in a single request

### Sync Lines - Create only (new empty lines)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/carbon-inventories/1/lines/sync HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "create": [
    {
      "subcategoryId": "1",
      "dimensionValue1Id": null,
      "dimensionValue2Id": null,
      "measurementUnitId": null,
      "quantity": null,
      "factorSource": null,
      "baseFactorId": null,
      "appliedFactorValue": null,
      "appliedFactorRateMeasurementUnitId": null,
      "manualTotalEmissions": null,
      "comment": null
    }
  ],
  "update": [],
  "delete": []
}


### Sync Lines - Create with data (SIMPLIFIED mode - with factor)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/carbon-inventories/1/lines/sync HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

